"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-taylor-swift-olympics-2024-paris-b2585889.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Eras Tour singer is not scheduled to perform on the day of the Paris 2024 opening ceremony, which kicks off on July 26  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0224086980302608e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  TheParis 2024Olympic Games are almost here, meaning a number of famous faces are expected to attend this year's summer sporting event.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheOlympicskick off on Friday, July 26 withan opening ceremony unlike any before.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 10,000 athletes from around the world will take part in a 100-boat parade along the River Seine, withrumored performancesfrom C\\u00e9line Dion and Lady Gaga.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"C\\u00e9line Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}, {\"begin\": 836, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With some of the world's biggest pop stars set to attend the Olympics, many people are wondering what other A-listers will be spotted at the games - most notably,Taylor Swift.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Anti-Hero\\\" singer recentlykicked off the European leg of her record-breaking Eras Tourat the La D\\u00e9fense Arena in Paris, a 40,000-seat stadium set to host several Olympic sporting events.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1122, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"score\": 0.9929962766529531, \"rank\": 0.007053121458366404, \"text\": \"La D\\u00e9fense\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\"}, {\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6497748220057944e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Swift has since performed a number of sold-out shows in Ireland, the Netherlands, and the United Kingdom, she also has gaps in her packed Eras Tour schedule.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.8301978991061065, \"rank\": 0.1893517417841363, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6622452450643608, \"rank\": 0.5092867676361549, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1312, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8134690809148596, \"rank\": 0.21167407271601757, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 14-time Grammy winner is not scheduled to perform on the day of the opening ceremony, nor during the end of the summer games on August 11.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, she has a three-day break between her July 24 concert in Hamburg and her July 27-28 shows in Munich.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1590, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburg\", \"score\": 0.9379349392682366, \"rank\": 0.06617202641588939, \"text\": \"Hamburg\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburg\"}, {\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich\", \"score\": 0.9832597129531122, \"rank\": 0.017025294984744494, \"text\": \"Munich\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich\"}]}, {\"sentence\": 