", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swiftfamously made it to the 2024 Super Bowl in Las Vegasto watch her boyfriend, Kansas City Chiefs star Travis Kelce, beat the San Francisco 49ers.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2007, \"end\": 2025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kansas_City_Chiefs\", \"score\": 0.999506001860844, \"rank\": 0.0004801277021766356, \"text\": \"Kansas City Chiefs\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kansas_City_Chiefs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kansas_City_Chiefs\"}, {\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Travis_Kelce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Travis Kelce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Travis_Kelce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Travis_Kelce\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Shake It Off\\\" singer performed in Tokyo, Japan, the night before the Super Bowl - a 17-hour time difference.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2114, \"end\": 2119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.932307653834998, \"rank\": 0.07260730492779072, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2121, \"end\": 2126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.6489591617081615, \"rank\": 0.5364619336775857, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since Swift made the 12-hour flight from Japan to Nevada, it's certainly possible for her to take the less-than-two-hour flight from Germany to France.\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2230, \"end\": 2235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.6489591617081615, \"rank\": 0.5364619336775857, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 2239, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nevada\", \"score\": 0.9969770673577395, \"rank\": 0.003032098345004719, \"text\": \"Nevada\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nevada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nevada\"}, {\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9987210034471874, \"rank\": 0.0012682777606965502, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2333, \"end\": 2339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9787127280079917, \"rank\": 0.019716411801770393, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Swift has yet to confirm whether she will attend this year's Olympics, she's often shown her support for Team USA.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2351, \"end\": 2356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7332642317684592e-11, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}, {\"begin\": 2456, \"end\": 2464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9341986775335583, \"rank\": 0.0608735184680221, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last month, sheshared a selfie with the Prince of Wales, his children Prince George and Princess Charlotte, and her boyfriend Kelce.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2536, \"end\": 2542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edward_VII\", \"score\": 0.9261806540417078, \"rank\": 0.0797025990105796, \"text\": \"Prince\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edward_VII\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edward_VII\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In thephotograph, the NFL star was visibly wearing a black and white Team USA Olympic baseball hat.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2621, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9976182403620347, \"rank\": 0.0023813822413558637, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}, {\"begin\": 2668, \"end\": 2676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9341986775335583, \"rank\": 0.0608735184680221, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swift also has close ties with seven-time Olympic medalistSimone Biles, who will bemaking her return to the Olympicsas a member of the USA women's gymnastics team.\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2835, \"end\": 2838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.5892667425205701, \"rank\": 0.4907588737693512, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the 2024 US Olympic Gymnastic Trials, Biles competed in the qualifiers with anincredible floor routineset to Swift's 2017 song, \\\"...Ready For It?\\\"\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2980, \"end\": 2985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7332642317684592e-11, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, Swiftresponded to the gymnastics legendby reposting avideoof her floor routine to X, formerly Twitter, along with the caption: \\\"Watched this so many times and still unready.\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's ready for it tho.\\\"\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, after Biles withdrew from the Tokyo Olympics due to her mental health, Swiftshowed her support for Biles in a moving video tribute.\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3368, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the singer narrated theclip, set to her 2020 song \\\"This Is Me Trying,\\\" she acknowledged the public scrutiny that Biles faced afterannouncing her decision to leavethe competition.\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What do we want from our heroes?\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What do we expect of them?\", \"from\": 3586, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What do we need from them?\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What happens when they surprise us?\\\"\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swift narrated over clips of Biles performing on the vault and cheering on her teammates.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you have the attention of the world, everything you do takes on a bigger meaning.\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can be a heavy burden.\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can be a chance to change everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 3881, \"to\": 3922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swift concluded: \\\"Throughout the last week, her voice has been as significant as her talents, her honesty as beautiful as the perfection that has long been her signature.\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 4094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But do not you see?\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It still is.\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's perfectly human, and that's what makes it so easy to call her a hero.\", \"from\": 4128, \"to\": 4203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles, back on the beam in Tokyo.\\\"\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4204, \"end\": 4216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 4238, \"end\": 4243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.932307653834998, \"rank\": 0.07260730492779072, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles responded to the message, writing: \\\"I am crying.\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How special.\", \"from\": 4302, \"to\": 4314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love you Taylor Swift.\\\"\", \"from\": 4315, \"to\": 4340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4326, \"end\": 4338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4448108947192398e-57, \"text\": \"Taylor Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Bad Blood\\\" singer replied: \\\"I cried watching YOU.\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel so lucky to have gotten to watch you all these years, but this week was a lesson in emotional intelligence and resilience.\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We all learned from you.\", \"from\": 4527, \"to\": 4551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you.\\\"\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to Biles, the US women's water polo team are big fans of the pop star.\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4591, \"end\": 4593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"score\": 0.9999301429510864, \"rank\": 6.630043803107268e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medalistMaggie Steffens and her teammates attended one of Swift's Eras Tour concertsin Paris last May, the same stadium where the last three rounds of the men's and women's water polo tournaments are going to be held.\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4711, \"end\": 4716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.7332642317684592e-11, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}, {\"begin\": 4740, \"end\": 4745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6497748220057944e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We talked about it after [the concert],\\\" Steffens told theAPon Wednesday.\", \"from\": 4872, \"to\": 4946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had a team meeting of, like, if we get the chance to play in La D\\u00e9fense Arena, we want to be like her.\", \"from\": 4947, \"to\": 5053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to be able to love the pressure and be able to perform and have fun and enjoy that moment and make the most of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swift even gifted the Eras Tour tickets to the women's water polo team after her representatives were contacted by their team manager, Ally Beck.\", \"from\": 5179, \"to\": 5324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5319, \"end\": 5323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beck\", \"score\": 0.9999908800179816, \"rank\": 9.120065301967791e-06, \"text\": \"Beck\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beck\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As bada** and powerful of a woman as she is, for us to be able to see that in person was pretty magical,\\\" Steffens said.\", \"from\": 5326, \"to\": 5447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 5449, \"to\": 5679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5500, \"end\": 5511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2278751090291824e-20, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"